dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Shows roads, railroads, tourist and antiquity sites, kibutz, and  areas under Zahal [Tzahal] (Israeli Defense Force Administration). Includes: distance chart, key map index. Ancillary map: Negev. Scale 1:1,000,000. "Based on Survey material and approved for publication by Survey of Israel." המפה נערכה על יסוד חומר מחלקת המדידות ונדפסה ברשותה. Map continued on verso and overlap Negev inset.
